e of strong attractor for the\nstochastic moist primitive equations, improving the results, the existence of\nweak (universal) attractor of the deterministic model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Apr 2016 23:13:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 19 May 2017 03:38:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-22"}
