ng efficiencies found previously. The internal Mach number\npoints to the jet's energy content, and internally-subsonic jets are\nenergetically dominated by non-kinetic energy, such as thermal energy, cosmic\nrays, or magnetic fields.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Apr 2016 02:25:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 2 May 2016 15:00:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-07-20"}
