g new window for EB studies.\nThe remaining four IBs obviously have no connection to EBs and they do not have\nthe properties mentioned above, suggesting a higher formation layer possibly in\nthe chromosphere.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Apr 2016 03:50:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-21"}
