r most of our results, we give the extension to the\nD-factor which is appropriate for the decaying dark matter picture.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Apr 2016 14:42:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 29 Apr 2016 22:15:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-25"}
